description: Returns details about the IAM user or role whose credentials are used to call the operation.

nested_items.name: UserId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the calling entity. The exact value depends on the type of entity that is making the call. The values returned are those listed in the aws:userid column in the Principal table found on the Policy Variables reference page in the IAM User Guide.

nested_items.name: Account
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services account ID number of the account that owns or contains the calling entity.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services ARN associated with the calling entity.
